title: 2021 Week 10 Recap
itunes:title: 2021 Week 10 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap all of week 10 games starting with the Packers win over the Seahawks and the Saints-Titans narrow game. Nick Shook joins the show to talk about Tom Brady, the Browns and the Vikings. The heroes recap the Sunday Night Football matchup between the Chiefs and Raiders.
